  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluate the accuracy of the RTVue-XR and iVue for measuring the total corneal thickness, the
      epithelial thickness, and the stromal thickness in normal subjects and patients with various
      corneal conditions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
